==English==

===Noun===
{{wp}}
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{lb|en|biochemistry|organic compound}} a [[bicyclic]] [[heterocyclic]] [[phenol]]ic [[compound]], formed in the [[body]] by the [[metabolism]] of [[protein]] and [[excreted]] in the [[urine]] (or in [[faeces]], as in birds and insects)

====Synonyms====
* {{l|en|lithic acid}}
* {{l|en|rosacic acid}}

====Coordinate terms====
* {{l|en|urate}} {{lb|en|coordinate as a base versus an acid, but synonymous in the practical sense that the conjugate base and conjugate acid coexist in solution}}

====Related terms====
* {{l|en|hippuric acid}}

